of CDs on that were

00:47:15.980 --> 00:47:18.060
modeled on the Stradivari
instruments.

00:47:18.060 --> 00:47:20.080
This one is more
his own design.

00:47:20.080 --> 00:47:24.300
And Sandy plays, also, I'll just
tie that in, on a cello

00:47:24.300 --> 00:47:26.320
by Francis Kuttner
but much older.

00:47:26.320 --> 00:47:30.280
SANDY WILSON: Well,
this one is 1980.

00:47:30.280 --> 00:47:32.240
I didn't buy it in 1980.

00:47:32.240 --> 00:47:36.170
I acquired this just about five
